title.narrative: Contract Management Organisation (CMO) for Sindh Education Non-State Actors (SENSA) Programme

description.narrative: This activity (Contract Management Organisation (CMO) for Sindh Education Non-State Actors (SENSA) Programme) is a component of Sindh Education Non-State Actors (SENSA) Programme reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Procurement of Services' and a budget of £5,869,603. This component benefits Pakistan, and works in the following sector(s): Primary education. , with the following implementing partners: Oxford Policy Management. The start date is 01-08-2016 and the end date is 31-03-2021.
